{"tid":397842,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"就應山貓王巴打要求，整左個pesto pasta","createTime":"2017-09-12T18:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T12:36:21.000Z","uid":22793,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"067f1878b93b26c1823f92c8f641dc59f8ac2cd1","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T18:58:12.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次出煮野po,多多包含！<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/024142_2b2feda55d4bbea8cd71e725acbab65f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F024142_2b2feda55d4bbea8cd71e725acbab65f.jpg&h=a228b8bd&s={SIZE}\" /> 材料包括有松子仁，巴馬臣芝士，欖油，羅勒，鹽同胡椒適量<br />\n比例大概1:1:2:4<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/024413_eacaba6908edb95ad43b6f7aa0853225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F024413_eacaba6908edb95ad43b6f7aa0853225.jpg&h=083a2f98&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後就可以將全部野落哂blender搞，記得將芝士切到細細粒易搞啲，鹽同胡椒後落，芝士本身都幾重味，就住落！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/024725_1ada0c55b01c003d6f6a1d1d9b9c1788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F024725_1ada0c55b01c003d6f6a1d1d9b9c1788.jpg&h=f9bdf1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實用咩粉都可，烚既時落小小鹽同油，軟硬程度自己就，我就鐘意al dente,即係咬落去仲有小小硬硬地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/025023_f7ab66cf9d5a82242ca402b157a629a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F025023_f7ab66cf9d5a82242ca402b157a629a7.jpg&h=b1fbfd7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之我落小小欖油，再落一粒仔牛油兜兩兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/025140_8b506e5608ed13608de9ed2f800bd6a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F025140_8b506e5608ed13608de9ed2f800bd6a6.jpg&h=d113abb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啦屎記得離火先落pesto,太早落會變黑，pesto唔太受火。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/025306_05936f55b977fa22751f005292964e2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F025306_05936f55b977fa22751f005292964e2e.jpg&h=b2a7c11d&s={SIZE}\" /> 完成 bon app&eacute;tit<br />\n又可以依個人口味加入雜菌or海鮮。<br />\n希望大家鐘意，或者仲有咩想學，大家交流下，識整一定盡量整，多謝"},{"pid":"f4f2e33b96a0ed293579d0a59f25f90108f65067","tid":397842,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:57:04.000Z","msg":"我唔鍾意食意粉都覺得好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c3f42905cf8d4f66986b630631636b30fcc7ec","tid":397842,"uid":83118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:58:06.000Z","msg":"請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功"},{"pid":"44e1a10a275952dc8eaa5d59da00d274b2d5581b","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n可以"},{"pid":"9dee4fd7ede6502ab2c7dfd493e10e663d3a8199","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？"},{"pid":"00567a5480a593e4bc6d5bdecf3904a7ae9ee021","tid":397842,"uid":78613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:37:30.000Z","msg":"Thx巴打"},{"pid":"62111837c5905a2eb62b94bb7d6e4bed52bc9344","tid":397842,"uid":83118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔識講，整到一舊舊，唔滑，好乾，落多啲忌廉又好膩<br />\n卡邦尼本身可唔可以一次過整三人分量？定要分開整？<br />\n係咪我一次過整太多所以失敗？"},{"pid":"aa3104d2ea69fa7db8b8446e5830c1325b34dff5","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔識講，整到一舊舊，唔滑，好乾，落多啲忌廉又好膩<br />\n卡邦尼本身可唔可以一次過整三人分量？定要分開整？<br />\n係咪我一次過整太多所以失敗？</blockquote><br />\n可以一次過整，蛋王一定要離火先落，唔係就會變炒蛋。乾身可能你粉同cream比例唔岩，過兩日再開po"},{"pid":"df6a52a28401628e88965410e0f3f8e5ac5a6814","tid":397842,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:37:17.000Z","msg":"意大利菜？<br />\n定係法國菜？<br />\n好似好高級咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bae02e1e0d1181c2d2753f773ef699de9ea6e7","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T22:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意大利菜？<br />\n定係法國菜？<br />\n好似好高級咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獻醜了"},{"pid":"3ddc912de657288d8ce5b4c57ad1aa9fd4952efc","tid":397842,"uid":23916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173976e0692fb0a9dbb6d45765c7b530b4dc6892","tid":397842,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔識講，整到一舊舊，唔滑，好乾，落多啲忌廉又好膩<br />\n卡邦尼本身可唔可以一次過整三人分量？定要分開整？<br />\n係咪我一次過整太多所以失敗？</blockquote><br />\n可以一次過整，蛋王一定要離火先落，唔係就會變炒蛋。乾身可能你粉同cream比例唔岩，過兩日再開po</blockquote><br />\n我斬係整到大舊舊好乾  覺得自己落唔夠多意粉水"},{"pid":"861ca2d0fdc6e86c618f744416f007ac7f89090b","tid":397842,"uid":52714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔識講，整到一舊舊，唔滑，好乾，落多啲忌廉又好膩<br />\n卡邦尼本身可唔可以一次過整三人分量？定要分開整？<br />\n係咪我一次過整太多所以失敗？</blockquote><br />\n可以一次過整，蛋王一定要離火先落，唔係就會變炒蛋。乾身可能你粉同cream比例唔岩，過兩日再開po</blockquote><br />\n正宗係冇cream<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上youtube睇Antonio Carluccio同Gennaro Contaldo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800af772bf7e121d5ce6a3531afcf4fb0cec8817","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T13:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n點樣唔成功？</blockquote><br />\n唔識講，整到一舊舊，唔滑，好乾，落多啲忌廉又好膩<br />\n卡邦尼本身可唔可以一次過整三人分量？定要分開整？<br />\n係咪我一次過整太多所以失敗？</blockquote><br />\n可以一次過整，蛋王一定要離火先落，唔係就會變炒蛋。乾身可能你粉同cream比例唔岩，過兩日再開po</blockquote><br />\n正宗係冇cream<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上youtube睇Antonio Carluccio同Gennaro Contaldo啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正宗既係冇，但好多餐廳酒店都傾向有，冇咩所謂既，自己鐘意囉"},{"pid":"6d5d9f876b77c3bf0b8a6f039a796c0f912d0ae9","tid":397842,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下點樣捲到你最尾上碟咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8a1d0d29b894d7f4a6c1771091868e92c49efd","tid":397842,"uid":54197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"幾時再出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f35d906aef2f0a997b7de0f6b518d5d2baca7c","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/011156_0c5883e4901b90caa13ba5efa8f5bcef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F011156_0c5883e4901b90caa13ba5efa8f5bcef.jpg&h=32e13e9d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n用呢支差捲捲捲捲仲要係個煲邊扶住"},{"pid":"63363baea193d61556d5e75169e4a68ee1ac8d5f","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時再出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自家制 carbonara<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/399230/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/399230/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n出左了、歡迎交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba8317488c1ef91e5e4e07d208eba80291df169","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問可唔可以教整cabonara？之前試咗好多次都唔成功</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自家制 carbonara<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/399230/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/399230/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d15fd9c615d6b7b9335b41bf30e3bb8a52978f0e","tid":397842,"uid":92589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:32:06.000Z","msg":"我想問加雜菌嘅話係咪用嗰粒仔牛油炒香d雜菌 定係另外炒好先最後同pesto一起撈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4702669f073da73dc765cd7024166e2770577e35","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T20:59:19.000Z","msg":"可以用牛油炒香雜菌先，再落粉，啦屎pesto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b39ffb95d72e02874472d9b5d36de34c4b2a179","tid":397842,"uid":92589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以用牛油炒香雜菌先，再落粉，啦屎pesto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有時候我炒d蘑菇炒到出水 係咪咩地方做錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝巴打解答"},{"pid":"52959d6822464b9f9612eed2c49dc556a6c8a25d","tid":397842,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"pesto用Linguine好食Ｄ喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩服樓主自家制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我通常都係百佳買醬 返去炒兩炒算"},{"pid":"4222e64ee479b32a37a9cca124b589aabd604867","tid":397842,"uid":22793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pesto用Linguine好食Ｄ喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佩服樓主自家制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我通常都係百佳買醬 返去炒兩炒算</blockquote><br />\n用咩粉都可以，買梗係方便啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}